Webex App | Invite others to join you
You can invite anyone to join you in Webex App. They’ll get an email invitation that contains a link to download the app. If they can’t find the invitation, ask them to check their spam folder first. If it’s not there, ask them to go to https://web.webex.com to sign up.
Desktop
iPhone and iPad
Android
Web
1
In the app header, click , then select Send a direct message.
2
Type the person's email address and select Invite to Webex. After they join Webex App, they'll see your space in the app.